descript.abstract: Existing major-roads and freeways maintained in SANDAG's Tranportation database.
descript.supplinf:
SOURCE: SanGIS centerline road file; General Plan circulation elements of the local jurisdictions in the San Diego region; Caltrans State highway inventory (FUNC coverage); SANDAG Regional Transportation Improvement Program and Regional Transportation Plan.
The SANDAG transportation database is constantly updated to reflect the latest transportation improvements and plans for the San Diego region. New major-road and freeway layers will be produced when significant changes are made to SANDAG's transportation database. This layer contains existing freeways in addition to the major roads.
